Failed tests are not related to this patch. Please review.

```
4 failures / +4)
org.apache.hadoop.metrics2.host.aggregator.AggregatorWebServiceTest.testWrongPath
org.apache.ambari.server.security.authorization.AmbariLdapAuthenticationProviderForDNWithSpaceTest.org.apache.ambari.server.security.authorization.AmbariLdapAuthenticationProviderForDNWithSpaceTest
org.apache.ambari.server.security.authorization.AmbariLdapAuthenticationProviderTest.org.apache.ambari.server.security.authorization.AmbariLdapAuthenticationProviderTest
org.apache.ambari.server.view.ViewDirectoryWatcherTest.testDirectoryExtractionOnFileAdd

```

Hey @rlevas, I added you to review because I made a method in a resource provider public. Opening up the object oriented (the one that takes a ...Request object not a map) versions of the resource providers for internal use would be great (as it is a way more easy to create object instead of maps), however it bypasses authentication (which looks to be hashmap based). Please opine.
LGTM
